Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.38,0:00:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I couldn't make breakfast...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.\NYou have such a high fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.97,0:00:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You keep resting.\NI'll call school for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.02,0:00:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to make dinner, either.\NStay in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.56,0:00:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otosaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.07,0:00:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, Otosaka was absent with a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kato.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.94,0:00:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.78,0:00:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kijima.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.70,0:00:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.66,0:00:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.61,0:00:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Konishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.49,0:00:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Komatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Komiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:18.97,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 6\NHappy You\NDid Not Notice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.82,0:02:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The ability is... collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Collapse? What kind of ability is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Probably something like\N"able to destroy anything they target."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:02:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The fact that it's not "destruction"\Nis kinda scary.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:02:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, where's this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:03:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is our condo complex\Nthat is attached to this academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.64,0:03:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, isn't it natural\Nfor someone with an ability to be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This person is in their \Ncondo right now, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that's strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Parents will not be wielders \Nof special abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as it only occurs during adolescence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.86,0:03:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The target is home sick from school,\Nor something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Impossible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, that's an abnormal bit of agitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's a coincidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Try talking to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My little sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...is bedridden with a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It might be that both siblings \Nshow these symptoms after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're no scientists,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so let's go visit Ayumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and see if she really\Ngained a special ability while we're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, are all of you going?\NWe're talking about a sick girl here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess I'll go by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, wait... Ayumi is a fan of Yusa...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I bring her along,\NI'm sure Ayumi would be happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But you, fanboy, are getting in my way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want it to be just Tomori and Yusa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Should I take over his body and jump
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the window to injure him or something?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see... so that's how giraffes sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Giraffes wrap their necks\Naround into a coil when they sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, there's a giraffe here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I felt it senseless for him to come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nice going, Tomori!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a full-body protector on,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so he's fine as long as \Nhe didn't fall head first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have someone injured,\Nso please bring an ambulance right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the three of us\Ncan go visit the ill after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to buy a get-well gift,\Nso lets swing by a convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes! I want to buy something as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking I wanted to buy\Npackaged porridge packs on my way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.98,0:05:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, shall we eat the same thing as Ayumi\Nand have porridge for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You guys can eat freely\Nonce you get home, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we get in the way, we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We should all eat together, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm living away from my parents too,\Nso I'm all alone even if I go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to being alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but Kurobane just moved out recently,\Nso maybe what she says is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, Yusa isn't the only one...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I swore in my heart\Nthat I won't trust anyone ever again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I snuck out of that school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her parents sold her off to scientists,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and she no longer could trust anyone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:05:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and still is all alone....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The fact I have a little sister\Nmakes me more fortunate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. We can all eat porridge \Nfor dinner together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your total is 1360 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This goes over my budget.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.83,0:06:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh I'll pay for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And these, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why stewed enoki mushrooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't stewed enoki mushrooms the best?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect on top of porridge, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's just your personal tastes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,well, I don't care\Nas long as you're paying for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm fine with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, that can of cookies back there...\Ncan I have that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've never seen anyone buy that before!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It will be 2500 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it's expensive!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To top it off, what is this paper bag?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.48,0:06:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I've never seen this paper bag, either!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:06:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My little sister is a \Npretty huge fan of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me look forward\Nto seeing her even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She is currently in bed with a fever...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we can't get her too excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the least, she will get a nosebleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like things to be gradual,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,like "Hey? Can that really be Yusarin?"\Nor something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll have my disguise mask on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Then, can you \Nhang out here for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Guests? Who are they?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother Yu is home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, elder brother sir, sorry to be intruding!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nomura, the class representative!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We came here in order to visit Ayucchi\Nwhile she's sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Oikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your little sister is allowing \Nme to be her friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is a pleasure meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can your brown-nosing\Nbe more obvious than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You already got denied once.\NAyucchi will hate you even more if you do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So this is the guy\Nthat asked Ayumi out and got dumped..?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to barge in with so many people!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, both of you, let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Elder brother sir, sorry to be so rowdy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And Ayucchi, get better soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! Excuse me, or rather,\Nsorry for coming in already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I didn't call for you yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was just a personnel swap....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Big Sister Tomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You got to see me again, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can it be that you're now\NBig Brother's girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you guys make a good couple...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well... we have one more guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yu sa ri n...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She saw through me instantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop her bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to breathe from your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There, it stopped now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yu sa ri n...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop her bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Should I cast my magic charm\Nthat stops nosebleeds?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.11,0:09:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I think it will do the opposite\Nof what you intend, so please don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yusarin in the flesh. Boy, was I surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You finally calmed down?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, these are some cookies\Nas a get-well gift. I'll leave them here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way! I made Yusarin worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's nothing more\Nthan one of my classmates right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think about it too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her speech patterns\Nare starting to catch on already...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the get-well gift from me is... this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I love those!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have an appetite?\NWe bought some pouched porridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Big Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're eating porridge, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Porridge for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.19,0:10:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's super-duper-delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it? Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the meal...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the hard work.\NYes... Yes, I understand. Excuse me now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, I have to go work now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're talking to a current showbiz celebrity.\NDon't complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is exactly correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please do your best at your work!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! With that, I'll be going now.\NAyumi, please get better soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:11:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yusarin! Thank you so much for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gratitude and thankfulness\Nfalling like rain and hail!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess we'll clean up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to wash them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can wash this many dishes\Nat any point in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What blood type are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm washing it now.\NYou can at least dry them with a dishcloth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you two really might be dating\Nand keeping it a secret from Ayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That won't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You two are so compatible!\NIs that how you hide your bashfulness?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're seriously wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come now... Ayu thinks you two \Nare totally a great couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Attractive and intelligent boys \Nlike this chump is someone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can never be a good match for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're such a good match\Nthat you're even too good for Big Brother Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:11:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't be fooled, Ayumi!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Realize that all the compliments are\Ncontradicting as she used the word "chump"!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, shut up and go watch some TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that was fast!\NYusarin moves at amazing speeds!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's pre-recorded...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.44,0:12:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, some medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.62,0:12:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You turn in for today. I'll tuck you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good thing you \Nhave a great big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I'm slightly \Nscared of going to sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.81,0:12:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had a scary dream this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you have a fever,\Nit's common for you to have a nightmare,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so there's nothing to be uneasy about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:13:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what kind of dream was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask something like that\Nbecause it will remind her of the nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll be going now.\NSorry to have bothered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am eagerly awaiting your next patronage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see her off. I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really, it's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please ask her what the nightmare was about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It might be a clue in figuring out\Nwhat the "collapse" ability is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. We still don't have proof that Ayumi\Nis the wielder of the special ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It can be someone else\Nthat lives in this condo complex...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is true that we don't have proof.\NBut, the possibility is very high.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And "collapse"... I can't help but feel\Nthat it will be a dangerous ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's the same terror that I initially felt.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, get it out of her.\NThis will be for Ayumi as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:14:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if her fever goes down,\Nmake her stay home tomorrow just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At present, we just have too few information.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.09,0:14:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell me what that dream \Nyou mentioned earlier was about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't remember it well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can just give me a vague idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A dream where something breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think... the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of ground was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.63,0:14:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't remember that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was like there were\Ncracks in the ground and splitting up...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be scary if that dream came true?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu is the type that doesn't believe\Nin spiritual stories like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The world is full of \Nspiritual things, though.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The ground splitting up?\NIs that some kind of a hint?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that ability is something
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so horrible that it will also \Nrope in the person using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We still have too few \Ninformation after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For now, we can use the large number
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.15,0:15:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of surveillance cameras set \Nup at the middle school
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to see which way the ability is headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Other than that, probably just letting\Nthe teachers know to look out for Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The middle school has a lot of people,\Nso it's dangerous if something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lot safer at the condo complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to gather a bit more information,\Nso have her stay home again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Should I go cast a magic spell\Nthat cures her cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! Yusarin's magic spell series,\N#21! The spell for curing a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such a turn-off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, she'll get a nosebleed again,\Nso I'd like you to pass this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:16:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, then I'll visit once she's better!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that helps a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,36.5 degrees... your fever has gone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu here has managed to \Nfinish fighting the illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and going to do her best \Nlike she usually does!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.31,0:16:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have a weird dream, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.68,0:16:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you're still recovering.\NI think you should stay home for one more day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's boring to stay in bed even without a fever,\Nso I'd like to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's still a chance that \Nyour cold will relapse,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.81,0:16:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I can't allow that as your big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Suck it up, be a good girl,\Nand stay in bed for one more day. Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll contact your school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu is not so easy\Nthat you can stop her time and time again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The grudge of the pizza sauce...\Nwill be avenged!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are your injuries all better already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mean when I was pushed off\Nfrom the student council room two days ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.54,0:17:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.16,0:17:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's something that happens often,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so accidents of that level \Ncan be dealt with right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Though, when I first met her,\Nit really was an instant trip to the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I was in your shoes,\NI'd never be able to deal with it all...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It really makes me slightly unsure\Nof whether or not Tomori should be the leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She is a lot more calculating\Nthan what you're currently thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's calling us over again.\NLet's hurry up and eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Both of use were eating pasta,\Nso we couldn't wolf it down. Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did you find the time\Nto twirl a pasta around your fork to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi is at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I contacted her school\Nand made her stay home today as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How was her condition today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The fever was down...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I was worried about her relapsing,\Nso I told her to stay home for one more day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because her temperature is normal, perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She decided to attend school from third period,\Nbased on her own decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.68,0:18:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bad feeling about this.\NLet's go check Ayumi's condition right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice seeing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Otosaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found a sweets shop\Nthat serves really good red bean soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treat you some\Nto celebrate you getting better.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I just got better,\Nso I'll have to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.22,0:19:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If right after getting better is bad,\Nhow about we go on the weekend...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't get it, do you...\Nyou've been denied once already. Just give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way!\NI'm going to make my way back through from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.65,0:19:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.27,0:19:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do something with this guy,\Nso Ayucchi, you can go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Nomu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, hold on, O-Otosaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.86,0:19:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't stand a chance anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shortcut.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Konishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.30,0:19:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you showed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With Oikawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With Oikawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With Oikawa... I used to eat lunch all alone.\NWe were supposedly dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.69,0:19:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But ever since you showed up,\NOikawa... Oikawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.73,0:19:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if he's completely forgotten about me!\NHe looks at just you all of the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, let's talk it out!\NI'm sure it's just a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So put that cutter knife away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:20:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.42,0:20:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... you're going to see some pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:21:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Help... someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.34,0:21:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Someone..!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is... the collapse...
